    {
      "idx": 1,
      "text": "Tomorrow, our class will go on a trip to a mountain.",
      "para": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "text": "We will climb to the top and walk in the forest.",
      "para": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "text": "I will take my lunch and a hat.",
      "para": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "text": "“ Will it rain tomorrow?",
      "para": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "text": "” asked my sister with worry.",
      "para": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "text": "My mother looked up at the sky and said, “ The weather will be fine.",
      "para": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "text": "”",
      "para": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "text": "But just in case, I will not forget my umbrella.",
      "para": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "text": "Tomorrow will be a fun day.",
      "para": 4
    }
  ]
}